A simple parser for TMX files created using the popular 'Tiled' map editor.
See http://www.mapeditor.org/ for more information on 'Tiled'.

Implemented in the Pike programming language:
http://pike.lysator.liu.se/

At the moment, TMX_parser supports maps in CSV format only.
You can parse your TMX file and get a TMX_map object in one line of code:

    TMX_parser.TMX_map my_map = TMX_parser.TMX_parser("myfile.tmx")->get_map();

TMX_map simply aggregates all the data contained in the file.  All fields are 
public with extensive use of inner classes.  Hopefully the source code should
be pretty self-explanatory.

